HEADWORD: Unio
<hw>U"ni*o</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. L.
<ets>unio</ets> unity, union, a single large pearl. See
<er>Union</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of numerous
species of fresh-water mussels belonging to <gen>Unio</gen> and many
allied genera.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

